"        media: Ethernet autoselect (1000baseT <full-duplex>)\n"
"        status: active\n"
"        nd6 options=23<PERFORMNUD,ACCEPT_RTADV,AUTO_LINKLOCAL>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:417
